## 2026-03-29 - No skeleton/loading state during 300ms preview debounce
- Moved `setPreviewLoading(true)` from inside the `setTimeout` callback to immediately before it in both `useGeneratorPreview.ts` and `GraphPanel.tsx`. The spinner now appears as soon as inputs change (during the debounce wait), not after. Also added `opacity-40` with `transition-opacity duration-150` to the stale preview content area while loading, so the old data visually dims, making it clear a refresh is pending.
